  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Methylprednisolone Infiltration in Anserine Bursitis Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 2 Double-blinded, Placebo-controlled, Clinical Trial for Safety and Efficacy of Methylprednisolone Infiltration in Anserine Bursitis Treatment</official_title>
  <sponsors>
